Jenkins is that reliable, never-sleeping team member who listens carefully to instructions (pipelines),
 and automatically performs tasks exactly when and how you tell him â€” whether itâ€™s building code, running tests, deploying to servers, or generating reports.

ğŸ› ï¸ Daily Responsibilities:
Time	Task
ğŸ• 2:00 AM	Start build, run tests while the rest of the team sleeps.
ğŸ“¦ Any push	Detects new code, builds it, and runs regression tests.
ğŸ§ª On demand	Executes your choice of tests (PR, regression,healthchecks).
ğŸ“§ Post-run	Sends reports and emails to the whole team.
ğŸ“‚ Cleanup	Deletes old builds to save space.

ğŸ’¼ Skillset:
